summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the proposal of Judkins Park Development Corporation to purchase and develop Parcel 32A in the I-90 Redevelopment Project area and authorizing the sale of Parcel 32B to an abutting owner; authorizing the Director of Housing and Human Services to execute, deliver and administer contracts; authorizing the Mayor to execute and deliver, and the City Comptroller to attest to, the deeds; authorizing payment to the State of Washington of the purchase prices owing; and designating the disposition of sales proceeds.
